snippet.title: Polymega Gameplays - Elemental Pinball [PlayStation - PAL]
snippet.description:
Originally released in Japan, this is one of the smallest PlayStation games ever made in terms of file size. Other examples I can think of are SuperLite 1500 Series: The Tetris, Board Game: Top Shop and the US edition of Scrabble.

Published by Midas Interactive
Developed by Digicube
BIOS Used: Polymega BIOS
